truffaut ( french : les &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1962 french documentary film directed by françois truffaut and starring françois truffaut , françois truffaut and françois truffaut . it is truffaut 's directorial debut . the film is based on truffaut 's 1962 non-fiction book of the same name by françois truffaut . the film was selected as the french entry for the best foreign language film at the 89th academy awards but it was not nominated .